- Keep copy short, concrete, in the brand's tone; use __PYON_DISPLAY_NAME__ where the product name would appear.
- Every copy value MUST be a single line (no line breaks, no markdown headings, no \n).
- Dashboard/seed-post copy should match the brand tone (not the source site's navigation).
EOS
  local user
